data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and utility in this 3-bed, 2-bath home on 1 acre in Callahan, FL. Zoned open rural, embrace the tranquility of your surroundings. The property boasts a well-equipped metal workshop wired for 220v, catering to hobbyists and DIY enthusiasts. Two additional sheds provide ample space for work or storage needs. The converted carport adds versatility, now serving as a bonus room—ideal for family gatherings, man cave or as a game room.  Recent updates include luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout main living space, new HVAC in 2021, roof and water heater replaced in 2017.  Seize the opportunity to live, work, and play in this versatile haven!
